vaulthalla (0.34.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  - Added buffer release logic and improved exception management in FUSE service.
  - Implemented active client closure and improved the shutdown process.
  - Expanded system command implementation in shell protocols.
  - Enhanced install script with temporary source file handling and improved repository configuration.
  - Updated key file URL to .asc format and improved key handling.
  - Added new build and release badges to README.md.
  - Added CLI setup instructions and convenience scripts to installation documentation.
  - Removed unchanged Debian examples and scripts (prerm.ex, preinst.ex).

